35:15.332 --> 35:17.374
He had like John Rollins' job.

35:17.834 --> 35:18.895
Dow, D-O-W.

35:20.476 --> 35:20.677
Dow?

35:20.977 --> 35:22.398
K-L-I-N-G.

35:23.499 --> 35:25.641
